search for medicines, and access detailed information about vendors. The platform includes an admin panel that oversees user and vendor management to ensure smooth and secure operations.

Technologies Used: MongoDB, Express.js, React.js, Node.js, Docker, and Docker Compose.

Setup Instructions
Clone the repository:


git clone https://github.com/yourusername/PharmaLink.git
cd PharmaLink
Build and start the application using Docker Compose:

docker-compose up --build
Access the frontend at:
http://localhost:3000

Backend API runs at:
http://localhost:5000

